    "We construct the training set using these queries and their corresponding labels based on the responses.",
    "Similarly, we select 1,000 different queries from our dataset to create the testing set.",
    "In our knowledge distillation process, we utilize BERT [9], RoBERTa [27], ERNIE [36], and DeBERTa [15] as the architecture for the student model.",
    "The reason is that these models have demonstrated strong capabilities in processing and understanding natural language text.",
    "Additionally, similar to LLMs, they are all pretrained language models that have been trained on vast amounts of text data."
